WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.500
Compliance-restricted showcase.

00:03.500 --> 00:10.000
How to save $400,000 per year by empowering 790,000 users?

00:10.000 --> 00:17.000
The challenge at CASSI was to transform a confusing statement into a financial control tool.

00:17.000 --> 00:24.000
We identified that the lack of visual hierarchy in the old statement obscured improper authorizations.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
We redesigned the information architecture with a focus on scannability and monthly breakdown.

00:32.000 --> 00:39.000
We implemented push notifications with immediate action buttons for procedure disputes.

00:39.000 --> 00:48.000
We optimized the UX for dependents with gesture-based profile switching, eliminating the need for a new login.

00:48.000 --> 00:57.000
We reduced accessibility technical debt by 47%, ensuring compliance with WCAG standards.

00:57.000 --> 01:15.000
The impact: 13,000 disputes and over $400,000 saved per year, according to page 38 of the 2022 annual public report.